kye; rgyal ba'i sras dag/ bcu po 'di rnams ni/ byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po dag gi ting nge 'dzin gyi bye brag la 'jug pa'i ye shes so/ /
kye; rgyal ba'i sras dag /bcu po 'di rnams ni/ byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po rnams kyi ting nge 'dzin rgya chen por bya ba la mkhas pa ste/ bcu gang zhe na/ 'di lta ste/ kye; rgyal ba'i sras dag/ 'di la byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen pos stong gsum gyi stong chen po'i 'jig rten gyi khams pad+mo gcig tu byin gyis brlabs te/ pad+mo gcig po de rang gi skyil mo krung gis rgyas par khyab par byin gyis rlob bo/ / rang gi lus de las kyang stong gsum gyi stong chen po'i 'jig rten gyi khams ston to/ / stong gsum gyi stong chen po'i 'jig rten gyi khams der yang gling bzhi pa khrag khrig phrag brgya ston to; ; gling bzhi pa khrag khrig brgya po re re zhing yang bdag gi lus re re byin gyis rlob ste/ lus de dag re re la'ang stong gsum gyi stong chen po'i 'jig rten gyi khams khrag khrig brgya brgya ston to/ / 'jig rten gyi khams de dag gi gling bzhi pa re rer yang byang chub sems dpa'i spyod pa khrag khrig brgya brgya yang dag par ston te/ byang chub sems dpa'i spyod pa de dag re re la yang mos pa bye ba khrag khrig brgya brgya mngon par bsgrub bo/ / mos pa de dag re re la'ang dbang po sna tshogs rnam par phye ba khrag khrig phrag brgya brgya yongs su rdzogs pa rab tu 'thob par bya ba yongs su rdzogs par byed do/ / dbang po sna tshogs rnam par phye ba de dag re re la yang byang chub sems dpa' khrag khrig brgya brgya phyir mi ldog pa'i lam gyis byang chub sems dpa'i chos la rab tu gzhog go /'on kyang lus mang po'am/ lhag par 'phel bar mi byed de/ mnyam par bzhag pa'ang nyams par 'gyur ba med do/ / kye; rgyal ba'i sras dag/ 'di lta ste/ dper na/ lha ma yin gyi dbang po sgra gcan zhes bya ba yod de/ de'i rang bzhin gyi lus ni dpag tshad bdun brgya'o/ /
de'i sprul ba'i lus ni dpag tshad brgya stong phrag drug cu rtsa brgyad de/ de'i lus phyed rgya mtsho chen po'i nang na 'dug kyang lus kyi stod gyen du 'phags pa ri rab kyi rtse mo dang mnyam pa dang / kye; rgyal ba'i sras dag /lha ma yin gyi dbang po sgra gcan de sprul pa'i lus dpag tshad brgya stong phrag drug cu rtsa brgyad pa des sngon gyi lus 'jig par mi byed do/ / sngon skyes pa'i phung po dang / khams dang / skye mched kyang yongs su nyams par mi 'gyur ro; ; lus chen po de yod pas kyang sprul pa'i lus la gzhan du 'du shes par mi 'gyur te/ lus snga ma shi 'phos pa'i 'du shes kyang med la/ gsar du skyes pa'i lus kyis kyang nyams dga' ba rab tu thob pa yin te/ sprul pa'i lus des mthu dang dbang byed par dbang sgyur bar yang yang dag par ston pa na rmongs shing 'khrul bar 'gyur ba'ang med de/ lha ma yin gyi dbang po sgra gcan de ni/ 'dod chags can/ zhe sdang can/ gti mug can te/ nga rgyal dang / dregs pa dang ldan yang rgya mtsho'i nang na gnas shing / rgya mtsho'i nang gi khyim na 'dug bzhin du rnam pa de lta bu'i sprul pa'i lus kyis mngon par 'phags na/ byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po chos thams cad sgyu ma'i rnam par rab tu rtogs pa 'jig rten thams cad na dpe med pa mig yor dang mnyam par rab tu zhugs pa 'jig rten gyi khams thams cad sangs rgyas skyes pa'i sprul pa rnam par dmigs pa lta bur khong du chud pa sgra dbyangs rnam par dmigs pa thams cad ri'i brag ca lta bur shes pa yang dag pa'i chos rab tu mthong ba/ chos ji lta ba bzhin gyi lus dang ldan pa/ rang bzhin gyis 'od gsal zhing dang ba'i chos la zhugs pa/ sems kyi rang bzhin dngos po med par rab tu rtogs pa/ lus kyi yul tshad med pa la gnas pa/ sangs rgyas kyi ye shes snang bas byang chub kyi spyod pa rnam par sbyangs pa lta smos kyang ci dgos te;

What are the ten?
One, explanation not violating meaning;
two, inexhaustibility of teaching;
three, impeccable expression;
four, endless eloquence;
five, freedom from hesitation;
six, truthfulness of speech;
seven, the trust of the community;
eight, liberating those in the triple world;
nine, supreme excellence of roots of goodness;
ten, command of the wondrous Teaching.
These are the ten anointments.

'di lta ste/ dper na/ klu'i rgyal po chen po ma dros pa'i gnas nas chu klung chen po ma dros pa rnyog pa med pa; dang ba 'od gsal ba/ dri ma med pa dag pa/ nam mkha' lta bu dri ma dang bral ba bzhi 'bab ste/ de dag kyang kha gcig dang / gnyis dang / gsum dang / bzhi'i sgo nas 'bab ste/ 'di ltar chu klung chen po gang+gA ni glang po che'i kha nas 'bab bo/ / chu klung chen po si ta ni seng ge'i kha nas 'bab bo/ / chu klung chen po sin+d+hu ni glang gi kha nas 'bab bo/ / chu klung chen po pak+Shu ni rta'i kha nas 'bab bo/ / de dag de ltar phyogs bzhi nas kha'i sgo bzhi nas 'bab ste/ chu klung gang+gA ni dngo nas dngul gyi bye ma 'dren cing 'bab ste/ dngul gyi bye ma la gnas so/ / chu klung si ta ni dngo nas rdo rje'i bye ma 'dren cing 'bab ste/ / rdo rje'i bye ma la gnas so/ / chu klung chen po sin+d+hu ni dngo nas gser gyi bye ma 'dren cing 'bab ste/ gser gyi bye ma la gnas so/ / chu klung chen po pak+Shu ni dngo nas bai DUr+ya'i sngon po'i bye ma 'dren cing 'bab ste/ bai DUr+ya sngon po'i bye ma la gnas so/ / chu klung chen po gang+gA ni lha rdzas kyi dngul gyi kha dog lta bu'i sgo nas 'bab bo; ;
chu klung chen po si ta ni lha rdzas kyi rdo rje'i kha dog lta bu'i sgo nas 'bab bo/ / chu klung chen po sin+d+hu ni lha rdzas kyi gser gyi kha dog lta bu'i sgo nas 'bab bo// chu klung chen po pak+Shu ni lha rdzas kyi bai DUr+ya sngon po'i kha dog lta bu'i sgo nas 'bab bo/ / chu klung chen po de bzhi char yang kha'i sgo dpag tshad tsam gyi tshad nas 'bab ste/ de dag 'bab pa'i tshe re res kyang mtsho chen po la lan bdun bdun du g.yas phyogs su bskor te phyogs bzhir 'bab cing / rgya mtsho chen po gangs chen mtsho la zhen par 'dong ngo/ /
de ltar chu klung chen po rnams kyis lan bdun du g.yas phyogs su bskor ba'i bar gyi gling de dag kyang / me tog ut+pa la dang / pad mo dang / ku mu da dang / puN+Da ri ka dang / lha rdzas kyi rin po che'i rang bzhin las grub pa/ yid du 'ong ba dri zhim pa/ mtha'i rgyan du sdug pa/ mdog gsal ba/ rin po che sna tshogs kyi kha dog ltar 'dug pa/ 'od dang zhing gsal ba/ gcig gis gzugs brnyan gcig tu snang ba/ mdangs dga' ba/ blta na yid du 'ong ba/ rang bzhin dang zhing shin tu rnam par dag pas brgyan pa ste/ blta na kha dog 'od gsal ba/ mun bsal cing snang ba 'byin pa/ blta na gting mi bra zhing shin tu rnam par phye bar brgyan pa/ kha dog sna tshogs su me tog gis kun nas yogs pa/ 'dab ma sna tshogs dang ldan zhing; snying po kha dog sna tshogs can/ ze ba mdog du mar snang ba'i me tog gis yongs su brgyan pa ste/ mtsho chen po de'i nang dang / mtsho'i dkyil 'khor ni rgyar dpag tshad lnga bcu yod de; zabs su dpag tshad lnga bcu yod do/ / de'i gzhi ni rin po che'i gseg ma bdal ba ste/ rin po che sna tshogs kha dog du ma dang ldan pas shin tu brgyan par gnas pa'o/ / de'i ngogs ni rin po che sna tshogs pha gu brtsigs pa ltar 'dug pas kun nas 'khor ba'o/ /

The unspeakably many pores
Each radiate unspeakably many beams of light;
In each of those beams of light
Appear unspeakably many lotuses;
In each of those lotuses
Are unspeakably many petals;
In each of those petals
Appear unspeakably many forms;
In those untold forms
Also appear untold petals;
In the petals are untold light rays,
In the light rays untold forms;
In each of those untold forms
Appear untold lights;
In the lights appear untold moons,
And the moons also manifest untold moons;
In each of those untold moons
Appear untold beams of light;
In each of those light beams
Also appear untold suns;
In each of those untold suns
Are manifest untold forms;
And in each of those forms again
Are manifest untold rays of light;
In each of those rays of light
Appear untold lion thrones,
Each with untold ornaments,
Each with untold lights,
With untold beautiful forms in the lights,
With untold pure lights in the forms;
In each of those pure lights
Also appear various subtle lights;
These lights also radiate various lights,
Untold, unspeakably many.

In each of these various lights
Appear wondrous jewels like mountains;
The jewels appearing in each light
Are unspeakably many, untold.

One of those mountainlike jewels
Manifests untold lands;
All of the mountainlike jewels
Manifest lands like this.

'di lta ste/ dper na/ bsam gtan bzhi pa la mnyam par bzhag pa'i dge slong gi lus kyi bde ba de lta bu dang ldan par gyur to/ /gang la las kyi sgrib pa'i nyes pa med pa de dag ni/ spos kyi dri de tshor ba tsam gyis gzugs dang / sgra dang / dri dang / ro dang / reg bya las byung ba'i nyon mongs pa thams cad byang bar gyur to/ nang gi dngos po'i nyon mongs pa lnga brgya dang / phyi rol gyi dngos po'i nyon mongs pa lnga brgya dang / 'dod chags la spyod pa'i nyon mongs pa stong phrag nyi shu rtsa gcig dang / zhe sdang la spyod pa'i nyon mongs pa stong phrag nyi shu rtsa gcig dang / gti mug la spyod pa'i nyon mongs pa stong phrag nyi shu rtsa gcig dang / cha mnyam pa la spyod pa'i nyon mongs pa stong phrag nyi shu rtsa gcig dang / de bzhin du 'phral gyi 'dod chags la spyod pa dang / 'phral gyi zhe sdang la spyod pa dang / 'phral gyi gti mug la spyod pa dang / 'phral gyi cha mnyam pa la spyod pa'i nyon mongs pa dang / mi shes pa de dag thams cad kyang byang bar gyur to/ /gang gis 'od zer spos kyi phung po gzi brjid rnam par 'phrul pa'i 'od rab tu 'thob pa'i don du dge ba'i rtsa ba yongs su sbyangs shing bskyed pa de dag gis gdugs kyi sprin de dag mig lam du mthong bar gyur te/ de dag gis kyang 'khor los bsgyur ba chu klung gang+gA'i bye ma snyed kyi dge ba'i rtsa ba bskyed par gyur to/ /de ni 'di ltar 'khor los bsgyur ba'i sa gser gyi dra bas dag pa 'thob pa'i phyir dge ba'i rtsa ba rab tu bskyed par gyur te/ de la gnas pa'i byang chub sems dpa' ni/ 'jig rten gyi khams sangs rgyas kyi zhing bye ba khrag khrig brgya stong gi rdul shin tu phra ba snyed du 'khor los bsgyur bar byed do/ /der sems can mang po yongs su smin par 'gyur ro/ /
'di lta ste/ dper na/ bcom ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs pa 'khor lo'i blo gros kyi sangs rgyas kyi zhing 'jig rten gyi khams me long gi dkyil 'khor ltar snang ba zhes bya ba de na/ bcom ldan 'das de'i sprul pa/ dge slong ba dang / dge slong ma dang / dge bsnyen pha dang / dge bsnyen ma'i gzugs dang / gzhung de bzhin du skyes pa'i rabs kyi sde'i khyad par thams cad kyis 'jig rten gyi khams tshad med pa dag tu mi 'gro ba de lta bu'i skad cig med do/ /thang cig med do/ /yud tsam med do/ /de bzhin gshegs pa de'i mtshan kyang grag ste thos nas kyang sangs rgyas kyi zhing der skye bar 'gyur ro/ /de bzhin du 'khor los bsgyur ba'i sa gser gyi dra bas dag pa la gnas pa'i byang chub sems dpa'i rnam par 'phrul pa shin tu gsal ba'i mtshams med pa'i 'od zer gyis phog pa'i sems can de dag thams cad kyang dge ba'i rtsa ba de dag gis sems can yongs su 'dul shing sa bcu 'thob par 'gyur ro; ;'di lta ste/ dper na/ tshad med pa'i bsam gtan thob pa ni/ ji srid du bsam gtan yongs su nyams par ma gyur pa de srid du tshangs pa'i gzhal med khang yang mthong la/ tshangs pa'i 'jig rten na bde ba gang yod pa de dag kyang myong ba yin/ de bzhin du byang chub sems dpa' 'khor los bsgyur ba'i sa gser gyi dra bas dag pa la gnas pa'i gtsug gi rin po che'i 'od kyis su la phog par gyur pa de dag sa bcu 'thob par 'gyur te/ chos tshad med pa snang ba chen po'ang rab tu 'thob par 'gyur ro/ /stobs rnam par dag pa'i ting nge 'dzin shin tu bsgrubs pa'i phyir mig yongs su sbyangs pa bcu'ang rab tu 'thob par 'gyur ro/ /gzhung de bzhin du yid yongs su sbyangs pa bcu yang rab tu 'thob ste/ sha'i mig rnam par dag pa 'di lta ste/ 'jig rten gyi khams sangs rgyas kyi zhing bye ba khrag khrig brgya stong gi rdul shin tu phra ba snyed cig rdul shin tu phra bar byas te/ rdul shin tu phra mo de dag byang chub sems dpa' de dag gis lag pa g.yon pas blangs te khyer la/ de snyed kyi 'jig rten gyi khams 'das pa dang rdul gcig bor te/ de ltar gcig nas gcig tu bzhag pa'i tshul dang thabs de lta bur bgrang ba'i tshul gyis shar phyogs su rdul de dag thams cad zad par gyur la/ de lta bu'i tshul du gang du bor ba dang / gang du ma bor ba'i 'jig rten gyi khams de dag thams cad shin tu phra ba'i rdul du blags la/ de ltar mang ba'i rdul shin tu phra ba de dag kyang khyer te/ shar phyogs logs su 'jig rten gyi khams 'das nas rdul shin tu phra ba gcig bor la/ tshul de 'dra bar phyogs bcu kun tu rdul shin tu phra ba de dag zad par gyur nas/ de snyed kyi 'jig rten de dag thams cad gcig tu bsdoms te/ sangs rgyas kyi zhing gcig gi chu zheng du gyur na/ lag na rin po che/ de la ji snyam du sems/ sangs rgyas kyi zhing de che zhing / tshad med la bsam gyis mi khyab pa yin nam;
gsol pa/ bcom ldan 'das/ de ni de bzhin te/ btsun pa bcom ldan 'das/ gang gis dpe bstan pa'i 'di thos par gyur la/ thos nas kyang glo ba ches shing ngo mtshar gyi 'du shes dang / rmad kyi 'du shes bskyed pa mchis na/ sems can de dag kyang ngo mtshar dang ldan par 'gyur ro/ /

kye rgyal ba'i sras/ gzhan yang 'di lta ste/ dper na/ ri dang / gcod rong dang / brag gi sul dang / mtshams nas sgra brnyan grag pa ni/ 'jig rten kun la'ang mtshungs par grag ste/ lus med cing bltar mi snang la/ gzhan gyi sgra'i rkyen la brten te/ sgra thams cad kyi tshul du sgra brnyan de dag 'byung yang de la rnam par rtog pa med do/ /
kye rgyal ba'i sras/ de bzhin du de bzhin gshegs pa'i gsung yul na mi gnas/ phyogs na mi gnas pa ste/ 'on kyang sems can gyi bsam pa dang / mos pa la rten cing 'byung ba med pa'ang ma yin te/ de ni sgras rnam par dmigs pa med cing brjod du med pa'o/ /
kye rgyal ba'i sras/ khong du chud par bya ba'i sgo gnyis pa 'dis kyang / byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen pos de bzhin gshegs pa'i gsung khong du chud par bya'o; ;

kye rgyal ba'i sras/ gzhan yang 'di lta ste/ dper na/ tshangs pa chen po ni tshangs pa'i 'jig rten na 'dug kyang 'dod na/ tshangs pa'i 'khor thams cad du tshangs pa'i dbyangs kyis go bar byed do/ /dbyangs de yang tshangs pa'i 'khor las gzhan du mi 'gro ste/ tshangs pa'i ris kyi lha'i bu thams cad kyang so so nas tshangs pa chen po ni bdag kho na'i don du tshangs pa'i sgra sgrog go snyam mo/ /
kye rgyal ba'i sras/ de bzhin du de bzhin gshegs pa dgra bcom pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyang / sangs rgyas kyi gsung bla na med pa sgrog pa'i tshe/ 'khor gyi dkyil 'khor thams cad dbyangs kyis mngon par go bar mdzad de/ dbyangs de yang 'khor gyi dkyil 'khor las gud du mi 'gro'o/ /de ci'i phyir zhe na/ de la de bzhin gshegs pa ni dbyangs kyi ser sna mi mnga' ste/ sems can dbang po yongs su ma smin pa rnams la de bzhin gshegs pa'i dbyangs grag par mi 'gyur ro/ /'khor gyi dkyil 'khor du tshogs pa'i sems can thams cad kyang 'di snyam du sems te/ bdag kho na'i don du de bzhin gshegs pa chos ston to snyam mo/ /de bzhin gshegs pa ni gsung sgrogs pa yang med/ phyir sdud pa yang med de/ 'phrin las de dag kyang yod cing snang ngo/ /
kye rgyal ba'i sras/ khong du chud par bya ba'i sgo lnga pa 'dis kyang / de bzhin gshegs pa'i gsung khong du chud par bya'o; ;

kye rgyal ba'i sras/ gzhan yang 'di lta ste/ dper na/ klu'i rgyal po ma dros pa ni 'dzam bu'i gling thams cad sprin chen pos rgyas shing khyab par bya ste/ 'di ltar lo tog bskyed pa dang / rtswa dang / gel ba dang / rtsi dang / nags tshal sna tshogs rnam par spel ba dang / rnang [?] dang / lu ma dang / mtsho dang / mtse'u dang / rdzing bu yongs su dgang ba'i phyir char chen po 'bebs kyang / char de ni klu'i rgyal po ma dros pa'i lus las byung ba ma yin/ sems las byung ba ma yin te/ sems can rnams la'ang rnam pa tshad med pas nye bar 'tsho ba'i rgyur 'gyur ro/ /
kye rgyal ba'i sras/ de bzhin du de bzhin gshegs pa dgra bcom pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyang / 'jig rten gyi khams ma lus pa thams cad thugs rje chen po'i sprin gyis rgyas par bkang ste/ sems can thams cad kyi bsam pa yongs su tshim par bya ba dang / dge ba'i rtsa ba thams cad shin tu bskyed pa dang / theg pa thams cad yongs su rdzogs par bya ba'i phyir chos kyi sprin chen po'i char bdud rtsi'i ro dang ldan pa 'bebs te/ de bzhin gshegs pa'i gsung de yang nang nas byung ba yang ma yin/ phyi rol nas 'byung ba yang ma yin mod kyi/ de ltar tshad med pa'i sems can rnams kyang nye bar 'tsho ba'i rgyur 'gyur ro/ /
kye rgyal ba'i sras/ khong du chud par bya ba'i sgo bdun pa 'dis kyang / de bzhin gshegs pa'i gsung khong du chud par bya'o; ;

“There is also a water spirit Ten Light Beams, which rains even more water than that into the ocean;
the water spirit Hundred Light Beams rains even more water than that into the ocean;
the water spirits Magnificent Arrays, Thoughtful, Thundering, Joy, Infinite Light, Continuous Shower, Great Victory, Great Surge, and eight billion more such water spirits each rain more and more into the ocean;
the son of the water spirit Ocean, named Rose Apple Banner, rains even more than that.
